## Extinct Races

Several races have vanished over the ages:
- **Dwemer** — disappeared during the Battle of Red Mountain (1E 700)
- **Ayleids** — the Wild Elves of Cyrodiil, wiped out by the Alessian Revolt
- **Falmer** — the Snow Elves, enslaved by the Dwemer and degenerated into blind creatures
- **Left-Handed Elves** — destroyed by the Redguards on Yokuda
- **Nedes** — proto-human ancestors absorbed into modern populations
